quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,119,"Besekuthi ngempela iNkosi yakho kulabo abenza okubi ngokungazi bese beyazisola (bacele intethelelo kuMvelinqangi) emva kwalokho bese bayazilungisa, ngempela iNkosi yakho emva kwalokho iyathethelela inesihawu"
  16,120,"Ngempela u-Abrahamu wayengumholi emhlonipha uMvelinqangi, eqotho futhi wayengesiyena omunye wabakhonza izithixo"
  16,121,"Wayengobongayo mayelana nobubele (ayenzelwe bona nguMvelinqangi), (uMvelinqangi) wamkhetha futhi wamholela endleleni eqondile"
  16,122,Futhi samnika okuhle lapha emhlabeni futhi ngempela yena empilweni ezaya uyokuba ngomunye wabalungileyo
  16,123,Sabe sesithumela kuwena isembulo (sathi) “landela inkolo ka- Abrahamu oqotho futhi wayengesiyena omunye wabakhonzi bezithixo”
  16,124,Kuphela isabatha lalibekelwe labo ababephikisana ngalo futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho iyokwehlulela phakathi kwabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo mayelana nalokho ababephikisana ngakho
  16,125,Memela endleleni yeNkosi yakho ngobuhlakani nangentshumayelo enhle futhi uphikisane nabo ngalokho okuhle (ngendlela enhle) ngempela iNkosi yakho yona yazi ngokwedlulele ngalowo odukile endleleni yayo futhi yona yazi kangcono ngabaholiweyo
  16,126,"Uma nijezisa, ngakho-ke jezisani ngokulinganayo nalokho enanijeziswe ngakho, kepha uma nibekezela ngempela kungcono kwababekezelayo"
  16,127,"Futhi bekezela, ukubekezela kwakho angeke kube khona ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi ungaphatheki kabi ngabo futhi ungaphatheki kabi ngenxa yalokho abakucebayo"
  16,128,Ngempela uMvelinqangi ukanye nalabo abenza okulungileyo kanye nalabo abangabenzi bokuhle